ZScore_Overnight_Shock_20D.expression: ZSCORE(($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_MEAN(MAX($high - $low, MAX(ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1)), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1)))), 20) + 1e-8))

ISEC_Factor_3_5D.expression: SIGN($open / DELAY($close, 1) - 1) * TS_MEAN(($low - TS_MIN($low, 5)) / ($high - $low + 1e-8), 3) * TS_CORR(TS_PCTCHANGE($close, 1), DELTA($volume, 1), 5)

Z_Informed_Breakout_Ranked.expression: RANK(TS_SUM($volume, 10) / (TS_MAX($high, 10) - TS_MIN($low, 10) + 1e-8)) * RANK(($low - TS_MIN($close, 5)) / ($high - $low + 1e-8)) * SIGN($open - DELAY($close, 1))

Smoothed_Gap_Residual_Alpha_5D.expression: TS_SUM(($close / DELAY($close, 1) - 1) - MEAN($close / DELAY($close, 1) - 1), 5) * SMA(($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / ($high - $low + 1e-8), 5, 1)

Ranked_Information_Shock_Persistence.expression: RANK(TS_RANK(($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_MEAN(MAX($high - $low, MAX(ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1)), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1)))), 20) + 1e-8), 10))

Gap_Intraday_Intensity_Reversal_20D.expression: (($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (DELAY($close, 1) + 1e-8)) * TS_ZSCORE(($high - $low) / (TS_MEAN(MAX(MAX($high - $low, ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1))), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1))), 20) + 1e-8), 20)

Institutional_Exhaustion_Reversal_10D.expression: (RANK(TS_PCTCHANGE($close, 10)) - RANK(TS_MEAN(TS_PCTCHANGE($close, 1) * $volume, 10))) * (ABS($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_MEAN(MAX($high - $low, MAX(ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1)), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1)))), 10) + 1e-8))

VASRF_Stealth_Accumulation_20D.expression: TS_CORR($close, $volume, 20) * INV(TS_CORR($high - $low, $volume, 10) + 1e-8) * (TS_MEAN(MAX($high - $low, MAX(ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1)), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1)))), 14) / (TS_MEAN($close, 14) + 1e-8))

Ranked_Idio_Gap_Stability_5D.expression: RANK(TS_SUM(REGRESI($close / DELAY($close, 1) - 1, MEAN($close / DELAY($close, 1) - 1), 1), 5)) * RANK(($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_STD($close, 5) + 1e-8))

Volatility_Adjusted_Gap_Conviction.expression: (ABS($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_MEAN(MAX(MAX($high - $low, ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1))), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1))), 20) + 1e-8)) / (($high - $low) / (TS_MEAN(MAX(MAX($high - $low, ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1))), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1))), 20) + 1e-8) + 1e-8)
